descript.abstract: This dataset, prepared for use in the Interactive Atlas of Indonesia's Forests (2009), displays the boundaries of the countries surrounding Indonesia. It was derived from the ESRI product named "Countries 2006" (ESRI Data and Maps, 2006). The World Resources Institute modified the boundaries of the countries bordering Indonesia slightly to fit with the boundaries of Indonesia, using the national boundaries data produced by Badan Pusat Statistik (BPS) in 2003.
